#### If the user does not select any subjects

Say ‘Select if you taught Biology, Chemistry, Physics, Computing, Languages or
if you did not teach any of these subjects’.

If you have a longer list of subjects you consider saying 'Select which subjects
you taught or select that you did not teach any of these subjects'

### Research on this component

#### Teachers work in academic years

If you need to ask which subjects a teacher taught during the tax year or any
other timeframe, it may be more difficult for teachers to think about and answer
correctly.

Teachers who change jobs tend to do so between academic years or at the end of a
term. Teachers are more likely to have worked at more than one school, held more
than one position, or taught more than one subject in a tax year or any other
given timeframe compared to a single academic year.
